Purpose
This file is the public facade of the library.

Linear intent
1. Re-export the core modules under one stable `Core` namespace so callers do not need to know every internal file name.
2. Re-export the configuration loader under `Config` to keep the external API organized.
3. Re-export the agent modules under `Agents` so users can discover the built-in agents from one place.
4. Re-export the runtime modules under `Runtime` so operational pieces like logging and retries stay visible but grouped.
5. Re-export the orchestration modules under `Orchestration` so the routing layer is accessible without exposing the whole file tree.
6. Provide a single high-level `run` function for the common case.
7. Build the default registry inside `run` so the caller gets a working system without manual registration.
8. Build an empty typed context with task id and metadata.
9. Start the orchestrator with the initial payload wrapped as `Core_payload.Text`.

